    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In The Flux Phenomena you find yourself in the secret facility of the once mega-corporation ARC-TiC Innovations.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your objective is to use ARC-TiC's proprietary technology, the ARC-TiC Innovations Portable Hand Held Flux Field Generator (AIPHHFFG for short or &quot;Flux Gun&quot; for slightly shorter) to complete puzzles, overcome obstacles and emerge from the bowels of their facility in one piece!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101960/extras/a594ebd7f552207e5ad86471f7d4c611.poster.avif?t=1762084484\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101960/extras/a594ebd7f552207e5ad86471f7d4c611.webm?t=1762084484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101960/extras/a594ebd7f552207e5ad86471f7d4c611.mp4?t=1762084484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through the vast underground complex of ARC-TiC's polar offices and laboratories with the help of your powerful but confused companion to prevent a disaster from consuming the planet<i>.</i>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101960/extras/f2af575c560879d50fe3f374549099e2.poster.avif?t=1762084484\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101960/extras/f2af575c560879d50fe3f374549099e2.webm?t=1762084484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101960/extras/f2af575c560879d50fe3f374549099e2.mp4?t=1762084484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Uncover the mysterious and confusing past of ARC-TiC Innovations founding, uprising and inevitable downfall.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ unique puzzle's</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fully voice acted storyline</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original Soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
